{
  "stem": "1765.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 227.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Morning, noon, and night, and-- and [YIDDISH], you know, on Sabbaths and on all holidays, we were all together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I-- it wasn't just noticing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a thunderbolt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In August '39, we were in the-- in the country-- dacha, it was called, you know, summer house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you heard a lot about wojna, war-- wojna is war in Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the end of August, my father, at the age of over 39-- he was 40-- he was born in 1899-- was drafted into the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Drafted, a Jew, at 40 as a foot soldier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we saw him to the train, and he went to war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the Germans were coming from one direction, the Russians from the other, and Vilna was in the middle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in 1939, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Molotov, who was, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think you would call him the Secretary of State in Stalin's government, and von Ribbentrop, who was in Hitler's government, arranged for a peace pact between Hitler and Stalin.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Vilna was given to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In other words, the Germans stopped just before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were in Vilna, but we didn't know where my father was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And finally news came that his dog tag-- you know, all soldiers wear an ID-- was found in a field, and it was assumed that he was killed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother, who had this incredible, incredible sense of ESP, said no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He didn't die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He will come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So everybody thought, poor woman, lost her senses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember when the rabbi from the synagogue came to call on her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She very politely said to him-- I don't remember exactly what she said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I remember the scene as if it was last week.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
